5c79ca5c62ae76364f95869e808a706a6ab3880f","tid":2395593,"uid":67454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"你咪試下靠實力去海外打仗，唔好靠人幫<br />\n立功立到做司令為止囉"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"佢識開Apache仲要去阿富汗上前線同Taliban駁火 比你呢個鍵盤戰士講到一文不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"佢個頭銜係司令喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇皇室光環佢做撚到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01a649c588a48769a68bde4edaac08effeeef03","tid":2395593,"uid":344173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"其實識打仗又唔係大晒<br />\n你估仲係以前斬咗幾多個人嘅頭落嚟就升幾多級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2658effd0b3844af1ca2f46744a754aaa671af68","tid":2395593,"uid":375135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aeb7452447a068523bd62bf9b6769646d1ce5e19","tid":2395593,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/paper/2021/02/04/11492107.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Fpaper%2F2021%2F02%2F04%2F11492107.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=d99b3b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國哈利王子，攝於2019年11月。(路透)<br />\n<br />\n英國哈利王子日前傳出計畫夏季獨自動身回國探親，每日電訊報2日接獲消息人士爆料指出，他已決心要保住自己當初被迫卸下的榮譽軍銜。同時，只要狀況許可，就會在英國花上更多時間。<br />\n<br />\n哈利與梅根於2020年3月卸下資深王室成員身分後遷居美國，皇家海軍陸戰隊榮譽總司令（Captain General of the Royal Marines）、皇家空軍霍寧頓基地榮譽指揮官（Honorary Air Commandant of RAF Honington）與皇家海軍小型船隻及潛水隊總隊長（Commodore-in-chief of Small Ships and Diving）等三個榮譽軍銜是少數幾個懸而未解的問題。<br />\n<br />\n報導指哈利同意放棄三個軍銜一年，直到王室今年3月審核他與梅根的地位時再行決定，但他仍渴望繼續保留不放。一位友人就透露，「對他來說，軍旅生涯是最重要的事物之一，當然想要保住了。」<br />\n<br />\n哈利1日打贏控告星期日郵報指稱他怠慢皇家海軍陸戰隊的毀謗官司，就表明他自認名譽與未來的關鍵繫於他與英軍的連結。隔日透過影像講話宣布永不屈服運動會順延時，字字句句都顯示他對英軍的支持完全沒有動搖。<br />\n<br />\n不過，外界普遍相信，既然他並未計畫重返王室，將別無選擇放棄榮譽軍銜。王室一位消息人士指出，女王一開始就明白告訴哈利，執行王室公務不能「一腳進、一腳出」，這個態度至今並沒有改變。<br />\n<br />\n報導還指，儘管王室在物色榮譽軍銜的替代人選，但哈利自認曾在陸軍服役十年，和「永不屈服運動會基金會」（Invictus Games Foundation）等組織持續保持往來，讓他在在都是最適合的人選。一位友人2日也指，哈利遷居美國後，若不是受到新冠肺炎疫情阻撓，其實根本就打算定期往來英美兩國以維護他與英軍的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121259/5230993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121259%2F5230993&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ESVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=72015ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121259/5230993</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"去KFC 做上校<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6809bbd727126b4943dcbb9bf47fe993547695ce","tid":2395593,"uid":109102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b666c98e7c679f5d82c0f7401d165bed50e44ca","tid":2395593,"uid":67454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1354ed4414290583bb90810a8007bfcd2f36b7ac","tid":2395593,"uid":109102,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"5c79ca5c62ae76364f95869e808a706a6ab3880f","tid":2395593,"uid":67454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"你咪試下靠實力去海外打仗，唔好靠人幫<br />\n立功立到做司令為止囉"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"佢識開Apache仲要去阿富汗上前線同Taliban駁火 比你呢個鍵盤戰士講到一文不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"你估我唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁軍功足唔足以做到司令位?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"唔足以做到 所以佢個title係榮譽 掛名司令無兵權係手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申翻 我都認同佢應該放低呢啲榮譽軍職"},{"pid":"b7364d7e0d89c27b0372afedbefafa1089d8c6f3","tid":2395593,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，攬住條臭西過世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb7ec53a7ae14b8443b29686cbb2021bdc8bf14","tid":2395593,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"其實點解會有得bargain?<br />\n一走就乜都冇架啦<br />\n<br />\n咁都得個個都走啦"},{"pid":"66124cea373a44229dc081c099f8de3c41996070","tid":2395593,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"應該取消佢所有同皇室有關既身份同收入啦<br />\n禁埋佢老豆比$佢駛"},{"pid":"0bc71b8e5117eb21105e64715ec2ad556c525c1e","tid":2395593,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"都幾十歲人, 唔好咁幼稚啦真係好丟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b2f2edcdbd0409c0914862e10cd9414f2b28c1","tid":2395593,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"聽隻雞枝笛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}